Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right you do abstain from alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably for the best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You did have quite a drinking problem
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you were drunk when you shot that boy isn't that right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've heard
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it matters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did is unforgivable drunk or not I have a few questions about what happened if you don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stefanios age 17
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what crimes did the child been accused
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so naive son
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours was a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He was old enough to rape and murder nine women and almost killed two more
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you executed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 40 of the UN convention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,States every child is presumed to be innocent until proven guilty according to the law
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you familiar with that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes of course I was I used to work in juvenile detention and article 37
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that goes you cannot impose capital punishment or life imprisonment without possibility of release on any person
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Symbol of the age of 18 you know that one
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The convention Agreements are considered basic human rights for adults and children alike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a fool do you take me for you really think I planned it all out in advance my shooting him was a drunken mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look I know that what I have done can never be undone all right
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I accept the consequences of my actions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to antagonize you I just want to cover my topic from every angle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry sir I really should have used more tact
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we walk the night air might do us some good
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to purchase the bottle please
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just something to take the edge off of the night air
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Dr Gillen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep calling him but there's no answer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Richard did say he might be getting to see Rosemary soon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But this hardly seems the hour for a father-daughter reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well when you finally do get a hold of him let him know how dangerous that young man can be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And tell him that I'm in route to his apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever look into Stephanie's background
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he grew up in an East German orphanage or something like that there's more to it than you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His crimes were to be expected
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew his past
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To a child like Stefan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That orphanage was hell on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good boy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But that didn't save him from the horror that might have even made it worse
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That orphanage devoured his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then picked its teeth with his soul
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The convention on the rights of children article 6 the right to life survival and development
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 8 preservation of identity Article 19 protection from abuse to Stefan the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So many fairy tales Eva
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no more fitting word for a place like that I can barely speak its name aloud
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,511 kinderheim steel sends a chill down my spine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So when will you be seeing your daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you answer the door you were on the phone with her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you see her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough talk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing research for my report
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all no damn it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on to you kid you're going to tell me what you've got planned for shoe Vogue
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So who are you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You got drunk and shot that boy to death that's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty of people did see you drinking in a bar that day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was after you'd already killed Stephen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of odd Mr Brown
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've researched this case exhaustively and try as I might I can't find a single person who saw you drinking before
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You murdered that young man not a one Mr Brown this charade has gone on long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you really drunk when you pulled the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You are quite sober
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:21:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are calm you executed stephanieos and you knew exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get it right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wake the mind when it wants to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you didn't forget maybe you're lying is it a lie you tell everyone around you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To lie you tell yourself were you absolutely certain he committed those crimes certain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To put him down like a rabbit dog you're guilty of murder do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad Boy's blood is on your hands how are you going to look Rosemary in the eye tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't her daddy a coward and a murderer hiding behind an empty bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well Richard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a drink
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr Gillen is that you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the police
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come here regarding your patient Richard Brown
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead
